Package com.kicas.rp.data.flagdata

Class TextMeta

java.lang.Object
com.kicas.rp.data.flagdata.FlagMeta
com.kicas.rp.data.flagdata.TextMeta
public class TextMeta extends FlagMeta
Represents metadata for flags that contain formatted in-game text. The format stored follows that which is parsed by the TextUtils utility.
